title: Lovable Gifts for Babies - Knit, Sew, Crochet
description: In many families, passing along a treasured baby gift to infants and their parents is a long-standing tradition. And when the gift is handmade, it's an extra-special gesture. In this book you will find gifts for newborns that are sure to become keepsakes in your own family, to be cherished for years to come. Instructions and patterns for projects include: appliqued quilt, cross-stitch birth sampler, an embroidered christening gown and bonnet, knit and crochet afghans and blankets, patchwork, candlewicking, huggable teddy bear dressed in a sweater, christmas ornaments, puzzles, pull toys, clothing, toy box and pillows.
